A ring of returning is a jade ring enchanted via the Lvl-2 Enchant spell. When rubbed, the player will be teleported to their current respawn point.

The ring will provide five charges before degrading to dust.

The ring will not work past 20 Wilderness.

Date Changes
31 August 2017
(update)

Partially charged versions of the item could now be turned into bank placeholders.

16 February 2017
(update)

The item's inventory sprite was rotated, so that unenchanted silver jewellery now has non-standard angles instead.
